data.description: Your mountain oasis awaits at this historic stone home situated on 3 ACRES in Laughlintown. Featuring original details like custom stone, built-ins & gleaming hardwood floors. The open-concept kitchen at the center of the home boasts stainless steel appliances, ceramic tile flooring & updated countertops. You'll love the enormous all-season room off the kitchen, which features stone floors, a wall of windows, gorgeous wood ceiling, and a pellet stove. Remodeled bath with jet tub & custom stone enclosure. Enjoy the peaceful retreat of your private yard, featuring woods, covered and uncovered patios, along with old fountains/ponds and other stone landscaping elements. One car garage. Newer water softener & UV system. Home warranty included!
